text.tspan: ZSS file format: detailed internal structure
Length and CRC are computed for this span
Data blocks have level 0; index blocks have level in range 1-63.
Payload format depends on block type.
Data payloads contain one or more concatenated, sorted, length-prefixed records.
Level n payloads contain one or more concatenated descriptions of level (n - 1) blocks.
Each payload is compressed, and then embedded inside a data or index block.
